<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    
    <hr>
    
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "ninja kiwi logo.png", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>
        
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%=skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
    
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I recently graduated from Cyprus High School as a valedictorian, and I am currently enrolled in the Code To Success program. Here is some extra text so that I can test the margins and how the progress bars will be handled within the About Me card area.</p>
        <p>Once again, here is some more test text to demonstrate the effects of multiple paragraphs on the organization of the card area. I am hoping that this will help to adjust to the correct layout.</p>
        
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controller="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Code To Success Bootcamp Year 1 (2017)
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 2
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              School 3
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>